data.description: Discover the perfect fusion of casual charm and modern sophistication in Lavon Farms. The inviting, open-concept of this 2020-built Meritage home unites kitchen, dining, and living areas creating a seamless space that's perfect for entertaining or everyday life. The kitchen dazzles with sleek quartz countertops, white shaker-style cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, travertine backsplash, and stainless appliances including a gas range. The chef is never far from the action with a center island and counter-height bar opening to the dining and living spaces. Ready to relax? Just slide open the doors in the family room to a spacious covered patio and private backyard or retreat to the luxury owner's suite with its spa-like bathroom. The Texas-sized game room makes a great teen retreat upstairs complimented by large bedrooms, a jr. suite, and plenty of storage. Live green & save with 110% offset solar, a tankless water heater, electric heat pump, and an impressive suite of SMART home features.
